<i>Lost & Found </i>anymore.

339
00:19:45.530 --> 00:19:49.460
But I'm working on a memorial issue
dedicated to Hannah Baker.

340
00:19:49.490 --> 00:19:50.590
I get that.

341
00:19:50.620 --> 00:19:52.960
But with her parents bringing a lawsuit.

342
00:19:52.990 --> 00:19:54.510
