What's the message here?

365
00:21:05.820 --> 00:21:07.860
What's the author trying to say?

366
00:21:21.370 --> 00:21:22.370
What are you doing?

367
00:21:23.380 --> 00:21:24.580
Hiding my contraband.

368
00:21:25.790 --> 00:21:27.420
