373
00:21:41.140 --> 00:21:42.990
Stay seated. hands on your desks.

374
00:21:43.020 --> 00:21:45.700
Study the quotation.
think about what it might mean.

375
00:21:45.730 --> 00:21:48.650
Relax. I don't think you have
what they're looking for.

376
00:21:52.650 --> 00:21:55.530
This is a complete violation
of our civil rights.

377
00:21:55.990 --> 00:21:57.380
Do you have a warrant?

378
00:21:57.410 --> 00:22:00.540
We don't need a warrant
on school property. It's for safety.

379
00:22:03.830 --> 00:22:07.040
They're tarot cards.
Want me to read your fortune?

380
00:22:07.380 --> 00:22:08.800
Okay. Mr. Jensen.

381
00:22:09.460 --> 00:22:11.590
You want to protest your civil rights?

382
00:22:22.810 --> 00:22:23.850
