383
00:22:28.400 --> 00:22:29.700
That's not mine.

384
00:22:29.730 --> 00:22:31.540
I need you to come to the office with me.

385
00:22:31.570 --> 00:22:32.690
We can talk there.

386
00:22:34.530 --> 00:22:35.530
But that's not mine.

387
00:22:39.450 --> 00:22:41.410
<i>If I'd known what would happen...</i>

388
00:22:43.500 --> 00:22:45.170
<i>what that night had in store...</i>

389
00:22:47.830 --> 00:22:50.210
<i>I might never have
walked through that door.</i>

390
00:22:52.170 --> 00:22:54.420
<i>But parties have a weird magic.</i>

391
00:22:57.470 --> 00:22:59.640
<i>They're like an alternate universe.</i>

392
00:23:06.390 --> 00:23:09.440
