395
00:23:22.450 --> 00:23:24.080
I like the hair. Looking good.

396
00:23:24.450 --> 00:23:25.540
Thank you.

397
00:23:25.830 --> 00:23:27.670
Keg's out back. Get on it.

398
00:23:28.330 --> 00:23:29.260
Here you go.

399
00:23:29.290 --> 00:23:31.380
<i>Maybe you do fit in after all.</i>

400
00:23:32.750 --> 00:23:34.010
Oh. shit.

401
00:23:34.300 --> 00:23:35.440
- Sorry.
- Sorry.

402
