437
00:25:19.990 --> 00:25:22.210
<i>And people don't really change.</i>

438
00:25:22.240 --> 00:25:23.320
Oh. shit.

439
00:25:26.030 --> 00:25:29.500
<i>Welcome to your second tape. Justin Foley.</i>

440
00:25:31.290 --> 00:25:34.220
It's an automatic
five-day suspension. Clay.

441
00:25:34.250 --> 00:25:35.680
