Principal Bolan. hello.

451
00:26:05.160 --> 00:26:07.130
I understand. Of course. Got it.

452
00:26:07.160 --> 00:26:08.160
Thank you.

453
00:26:11.040 --> 00:26:13.840
Principal Bolan feels.
given your spotless record

454
00:26:13.870 --> 00:26:15.640
