deferral program at the police station.

457
00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:23.760
I don't believe this.
You have no idea why this is happening.

458
00:26:23.880 --> 00:26:25.900
Okay. tell me.
Why is this happening?

459
00:26:25.930 --> 00:26:27.800
Who told you to check my bag?

460
00:26:29.720 --> 00:26:31.850
Do you have something
you want to tell us?

461
00:26:34.060 --> 00:26:35.850
