462
00:26:36.810 --> 00:26:38.980
Forget it.
You already think I'm lying.

463
00:26:39.610 --> 00:26:41.830
Look. I'm sorry. okay?

464
00:26:41.860 --> 00:26:43.830
About everything. all right?

465
00:26:43.860 --> 00:26:45.110
Can I go now?

466
00:26:46.280 --> 00:26:47.320
Please.

467
