471
00:27:09.640 --> 00:27:10.570
Three days.

472
00:27:10.600 --> 00:27:13.390
I told you they were doing a bag check.
Why didn't you hide it?

473
00:27:18.310 --> 00:27:19.310
Anyway.

474
00:27:20.400 --> 00:27:22.570
Didn't realize you were
