481
00:27:43.300 --> 00:27:45.420
I don't know what kind of person
anyone is anymore.

482
00:27:47.510 --> 00:27:48.510
Yeah?

483
00:27:48.800 --> 00:27:50.600
What kind of person are you?

484
00:27:51.800 --> 00:27:53.610
<i>Are you more of a beer person</i>

485
00:27:53.640 --> 00:27:55.180
