486
00:27:56.100 --> 00:27:58.900
Hmm... Tough call. Uh...

487
00:28:00.020 --> 00:28:00.950
I'll take beer.

488
00:28:00.980 --> 00:28:02.480
Excellent choice. madam.

489
00:28:02.730 --> 00:28:05.330
Tonight. it is being served lukewarm

490
00:28:05.360 --> 00:28:08.070
