491
00:28:08.570 --> 00:28:10.370
- Cheers.
- Cheers. Delicious.

492
00:28:12.660 --> 00:28:16.220
When I was saving your seat for you.
I had to fight off not one

493
00:28:16.250 --> 00:28:19.830
