496
00:28:26.050 --> 00:28:27.380
Oh. definitely.

497
00:28:27.840 --> 00:28:29.590
No fun on my watch.

498
00:28:29.840 --> 00:28:32.260
Fun? At a party?

499
00:28:32.890 --> 00:28:35.820
I'm pretty sure that's illegal.
Oh. my God.

500
00:28:35.850 --> 00:28:36.970
Oh. my God.

501
00:28:38.680 --> 00:28:41.150
Uh. you look really nice tonight.
by the way.

502
00:28:42.480 --> 00:28:44.190
Oh. This?

503
00:28:44.860 --> 00:28:46.940
I just threw something on.

504
00:28:48.070 --> 00:28:50.040
Well. you do. you look really good.

505
00:28:50.070 --> 00:28:53.120
Wait. wait. wait. I want to play!

506
00:28:53.240 --> 00:28:54.170
Scoot over. Clay.

507
00:28:54.200 --> 00:28:56.290
I don't think there's any... room. Whoa.

508
00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:00.120
